[QUEST78]
Nombre=Immaculate cane
Desc=Only for the best wizards of the Royal Army.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST79]
Nombre=Baston of the Eternal Night
Desc=Only for the high-ranking Wizards in the Dark Legion.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST80]
Nombre=Fragmented Grace
Desc=I was waiting for you, disciple. What many see as mere creatures... are not. Each one carries a fragment of an essence that was once pure... whole. Centuries ago, that light was shattered. Since then, its pieces have wandered apart... incomplete. Some tried to restore it. None succeeded. If you choose to follow this path, there will be no guidance, no shortcuts. Only fragments... scattered... waiting to be reunited. When all is reunited, return to me.
DescFinal=The essence responds to your call... and takes shape again. Not everyone understands what you just did... but I do. Don't forget: even the Light... can shatter again.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=29

[QUEST81]
Nombre=Dark Legion Shield
Desc=I can forge a shield for you, worthy of such a dark warrior.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=37

[QUEST82]
Nombre=Infernal arc
Desc=The best chaos bow available in this world.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST83]
Nombre=Empire arc
Desc=The best royal bow available in this world.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST84]
Nombre=The old Jacobo
Desc=Those damn goblins attacked my cart and stole my hooks. I'll never be able to train newbies without them! Recover them for me and show the world what it means to be a Great Angler. If you can do it, I promise to improve that old stick you call Fishing Rod with my fabulous old Jacobo technique.
DescFinal=That will teach those damn goblins not to mess with the fishing guild, excellent job!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=14
PosMap=34

[QUEST89]
Nombre=Excess dirt
Desc=I don't know if you've ever seen the sewers of the city, I wish you didn't have had that luck. But if you need some coins you could know the place. There is a fierce plague of rats that come to pollute the city and take refuge down there, if you want to help the greatness of Banderbill and get some gold, go and kill as many as you can, beware of the people there low, it is the hiding place of the worst kind of bandits.

[QUEST90]
Nombre=The bear and the maiden
Desc=There was a bear, a bear, a bear!, it was black, it was huge, covered with horrific hair! Oh, come, they said! Oh, come to the fair now! To the fair, he said. But I'm a bear. Black, huge, covered with horrific hair. And down the road, from here to there, from here to there, three children, a goat and a dancing bear! He danced around, all the way to the fair.
DescFinal=How sweet she was, and pure, and beautiful.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15

[QUEST91]
Nombre=Pecadada of the Royal Navy
Desc=Dagger for the best assassins of the Royal Army.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST92]
Nombre=Bloody dagger.
Desc=Dagger for the best assassins of the Dark Legion.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST93]
Nombre=Exterminate them as in Barad-Dûr
Desc=This will be simple, the lands of Argentum are riddled with orcs. You must kill a hundred of them to complete this mission.
DescFinal=This if it is unique, do not lose it.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=20

[QUEST94]
Nombre=Royal Shield
Desc=Soldier, your service to the Royal Navy has not gone unnoticed. Discipline and honor are the pillars that sustain us... and you have shown yourself to understand their value. Collect 10 Blue Badges and report to me. In return, you will be awarded a Navy Shield, worthy of those who protect order and the crown. This recognition is reserved only for Hunters, Workers, Bards, Bandits, and Assassins in service to the Navy. Do your duty, and you will be rewarded accordingly.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=23
PosMap=294

[QUEST99]
Nombre=Need for Leader
Desc=We have lost track of time, countless moons have passed since we crossed the entrance to this cursed labyrinth. Shadows stalk us, whispers in ancient languages ??creep through the halls, and the stench of decay fills the air. If you are the beacon in this darkness, defeat the Wandering Skeletons and guide us out of this hell before we are a part of it.
DescFinal=We are safe, you proved to be a true leader!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=18

[QUEST100]
Nombre=Black Lobos Infessed forests
Desc=As you have noticed in your search for wild boars it is impossible to enter the forest without being attacked by these beasts, the black wolves. They are larger than common, and more ferocious.
DescFinal=Thanks for your help! Here's your reward.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=14

[QUEST101]
Nombre=Full Moon
Desc=¡Mis respetos a tí, nadie lo habia logrado aún!
DescFinal=My respects to you, no one has done it yet!
RequiredLevel=16
PosMap=151

[QUEST103]
Nombre=Advancing for drainage
Desc=You have managed to eliminate the first defenders, but we must enter the depths of the Drain to get closer to the beast, complete this mission for me and see me again, I will give you a juicy prize.
DescFinal=Did you manage to see it?
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=17

[QUEST104]
Nombre=Guardians with upset
Desc=Part of the legend said that the beast's lair was protected by its guardians: the Scalecreepers; If you have visualized one within the Drain, this story may ultimately be true.
DescFinal=It's true! You will have to train very well to face the powerful Har Nareth
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18

[QUEST105]
Nombre=Legionary Shield
Desc=Legionnaire, I have observed your efforts in the name of the Dark Legion. Not all possess the discipline and fortitude to bear our emblems, but you could be the exception. If you can gather 10 Red Badges, trophies won in combat, return to me. In return, I will grant you a Legion Shield, forged for those who have demonstrated true loyalty and resilience. Remember, this honor is not for just anyone. Only Warriors, Workers, Paladins, and Clerics can aspire to bear this symbol of our strength. Go, legionnaire. Prove yourself worthy.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=23
PosMap=295

[QUEST106]
Nombre=An expert fisherman
Desc=So my brother has sent you, let's see..., let me see that rod!I see, it is of very good quality, but you will need something better than that to catch large fish. I offer you a deal!The fluids of the black spider that is in the drainage of the city provides an incredible resistance to the fishing lines. If you can get me a little I think I'll be able to make you a great cane.
DescFinal=Take this cane you can tell the difference in a very short time. But be careful, catching large fish will not be easy.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=20

[QUEST107]
Nombre=Family relics.
Desc=Come, I want to teach you something. This silver cane is a unique piece that has been passed down from generation to generation. I could give it to you if you fulfill a small order for me. A few days ago one of our fishing boats was attacked by pirates, we are all alive, but I have lost some very important family heirlooms for me. Hunt down those damn pirates, get them back, and I'll be indebted to you.
DescFinal=You've made it! With this unique silver rod you will be the envy of every fisherman.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=23

[QUEST108]
Nombre=Fishermen's guild
Desc=I see, you want to be part of our fishermen's guild. You'll need something better than that broken network for it. If you want I can improve it for you although I warn you that it will cost you a lot of money.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=30

[QUEST109]
Nombre=Har Nareth .. mythology?
Desc=Legend has it that an immense beast lives within the drainage, which terrifies the depths of this Castle. Are you able to obtain information? You should complete some missions for me, I can reward you very well!
DescFinal=Great job, but we must continue... Restore your equipment and talk to me again!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=16

[QUEST110]
Nombre=First landing
Desc=If you continue west, you can find an ancient island where Banderbill's expert loggers used to extract valuable resources. Try to collect information about the place and visit me again.
DescFinal=I'm sorry that you crossed those defenders, have this, it will serve to reward you in some way.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST111]
Nombre=Mythological deer
Desc=Thank you for your help, but I still need one last favor. I once heard a rumor about an ancient Mythological Deer that roamed this area, but I never managed to see it. His name is Cervus, if you manage to bring me his skull you will have an excellent reward.
DescFinal=This is the first time I've seen this, the legend was true!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=27

[QUEST112]
Nombre=Get out of here.
Desc=What do you want? Do you also want a swimsuit? Don't you see that I'm busy? Ten, take this list. Don't come back until you complete it and we'll see.
DescFinal=Congratulations, you've made it, this is what I promised you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18

[QUEST113]
Nombre=Minor problems.
Desc=Okay, now if I have a task for you. It's something I could fix in a few seconds but I can't leave my position. Locals report that a growing pack of wolves is brewing in the forests. Go and do what is necessary to stop this threat.
DescFinal=I'm surprised. Surprised that you took so long, did you get lost along the way?
Repetible=0

[QUEST114]
Nombre=Small and annoying
Desc=Goblins are even more brutal creatures than orcs... they are smaller so their brain would be even smaller, that explains a lot. But the reality is that when they get together they become a real problem since they love pranks. Teach them a lesson!
DescFinal=I hope they have learned not to mess with us, thanks for your help.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=9
PosMap=11

[QUEST115]
Nombre=Fangs at night.
Desc=I have a problem that demands someone you trust and you have already earned it. It's a dangerous mission, you may not survive but it's a risk I'm willing to take. You remember that time he sent you to kill those wild wolves, well, this is nothing like him. These creatures can devour you in seconds. Be careful.
DescFinal=You're alive! I knew you would make it.
Repetible=0

[QUEST116]
Nombre=Damn Murderers
Desc=I need to ask you a favor. I'm trying to head north, but the road is filled with these ruthless assassins who won't leave me alone. If you can clear the path, I can offer you a great reward.
DescFinal=This is for you, thank you for your work!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=9
PosMap=501

[QUEST117]
Nombre=Bandit Times
Desc=Goblins are creatures close to goblins, but they have a little magic in their blood. Help me eliminate them, they have been bothering my workers union and we need to achieve our next quota.
DescFinal=My lumberjacks will be able to work in peace. Here, I hope it helps you!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=9
PosMap=11

[QUEST118]
Nombre=Magical Horde
Desc=It seems a horde of little Goblins with great magical powers has invaded our forest, attacking the Kingdom's merchants. Eliminate them and you will be well rewarded!
DescFinal=With these potions you can continue training!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=9
PosMap=185

[QUEST119]
Nombre=Hungry Orcs
Desc=These damn Orcs started using Reinforced Bows to make hunting boars easier and now they've gone after the ones on my farm. I need your help as soon as possible to eliminate them and bring peace back to my Farm.
DescFinal=We will be eternally grateful!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=5
PosMap=188

[QUEST120]
Nombre=Trayoner daggers
Desc=Filthy rats. The dark elves used to know how to be our allies but their eagerness to stab in the back ended our friendship. Now they prowl the road between Ullathorpe and Banderbill, hidden in the shadows to assault clueless travelers. It's time for someone to put them in their place.
DescFinal=Thanks to you now the poor travelers can explore in peace. For now...
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=18

[QUEST121]
Nombre=Giant leak.
Desc=What do you know about ogres? No, they are not like orcs but bigger... They are much worse. You see, for a long time they were imprisoned inside Dungeon Marabel but someone (or something) released them and now the only thing bigger than them is their appetite for revenge. Revenge and human flesh. Be careful and do not get carried away by their size, they are extremely athletic beasts, you will see what I mean.
DescFinal=Are you still alive?! Ehem, I say, Of course I do, I would never give you a task in which your life is at risk... take this gold and don't ask any more questions.
Repetible=0

[QUEST122]
Nombre=A valuable friendship.
Desc=At this point I can say that people like you will always be welcome here. I will personally see to it that all the elf people know of your loyalty and courage.
DescFinal=What I give you is just a little bit of what your friendship deserves. Take
Repetible=0

[QUEST123]
Nombre=Mysterious Message
Desc=Have you managed to catch a mysterious bottle? Don't open it! I can offer you a great reward if you fulfill my fish order. Don't tell anyone about this!
DescFinal=If you ever catch a bottle again, don't hesitate to come back!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=16
PosMap=254

[QUEST124]
Nombre=Mule
Desc=Hello, young adventurer! If you manage to get 1 Mule Horseshoe, I can give you my mule to improve your transportation.
DescFinal=Now you can ride my Mule! When you are stronger, visit my brother Fabián, maybe he will have a better gift for you!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=20

[QUEST125]
Nombre=A very special assignment
Desc=Commission (description)
DescFinal=Commissioned (final description)
