RequiredLevel=12

[QUEST126]
Nombre=Some additional space 1.
Desc=What do you want to make a backpack with? Bring me the necessary materials and I will gladly help you.
DescFinal=It was a pleasure to serve you sir,Here is your backpack!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=30

[QUEST128]
Nombre=Palomino horse
Desc=Need something faster than my brother's Fighter Mount? If you manage to get 1 Palomino Horse Shoe for me, I can give you my horse in exchange to improve your transportation. Do not take this mission unless you are prepared to complete it. If you abandon this mission, you risk losing your current mount.
DescFinal=Now you can ride my Palomino! When you are stronger, visit my father Juan, expert Rider of these Lands, perhaps he will have a better gift for you!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=36

[QUEST130]
Nombre=The last mission.
Desc=You have no idea how much you have helped us but we still have one more problem that we think you can solve. This enemy is nothing like the ones you've faced before. In one fell swoop he can kill even the strongest dwarf. You must be careful but if you achieve it the reward will be enormous.
DescFinal=Wow! You really are a top-notch warrior. It is more you should be the one who stands guard here and not me. Well don't get excited either, that's not going to happen. Also, thank you very much for your help.
Repetible=0

[QUEST131]
Nombre=Immediate delivery
Desc=Listen, I've seen how you helped Elhandar and I'm surprised. I have a proposal to make you: I have received a letter from Ho Ka Rdum, an orca who lives on a farm on the outskirts of Penthar. We are not very close to those of her kind but she has proven to be trustworthy. It needs help and you're the one.
DescFinal=Go with this and tell him you're on my side.
Repetible=0

[QUEST132]
Nombre=Farm on alert
Desc=We have suffered a terrible invasion of orcs on our beloved farm, all our crops are about to be lost. Can you help us?
DescFinal=For the moment that's enough, but stay hanging around here, maybe I'll need your help later.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=6
PosMap=188

[QUEST133]
Nombre=Thank you very much for your help!
Desc=Thanks a lot! It would be my pleasure to give you your pay, but unfortunately I don't have it. That conceited elf of the Tree House is still indebted to me. Considering that he was the one who sent you here, don't you think he should take care of the reward? Go and talk to Lempard and tell him on my side that it's time to settle the books.
DescFinal=Are you back yet? It looks like you're really good at what you do. How? Does Ho Ka Rdum send you to collect your debt? Arrgh, these ogres think they can tell me what to do. Neglect, you will have your reward, I always keep my word. Of course, since you have helped Elhandar and Ho Ka Rdum so much, I think it is only fair that you now help me with some errands. I'm sure for a warrior of your caliber, it won't take long. Once you're done with all the tasks, we'll be done and you'll receive your pay.
Repetible=0

[QUEST134]
Nombre=A very valuable resource
Desc=As you may have seen, our glorious city of Penthar grew out of an old coal mine. Our coal deposits have been mined by many generations, so today there are not many left. Do you think you can help me get some coal to be able to supply the blacksmiths of these lands? I think 5,000 units will suffice. Don't worry, your effort will be well rewarded.
DescFinal=Thank you very much for your help! With these minerals we can keep the ovens on for a long time. Here's your reward!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=13

[QUEST136]
Nombre=Fire storm
Desc=To obtain the divine power of the dragons, you must face them, eliminate 15 of them and see me again, you will be well rewarded.
DescFinal=You have been very brave, with this spell you will always be able to carry the internal fire with you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=24

[QUEST137]
Nombre=Hunt for the Eye Watchers
Desc=The howling north wind brings with it a dangerous threat: the "Eyewardens," vigilant creatures with eyes like eagles who patrol the dark and dangerous lairs in the mountains. I ask you, brave adventurer, to venture into this dangerous territory to eliminate 30 of these relentless monsters and obtain 5 eagle feathers as proof of your feat.
DescFinal=You can feel closer to improvement, like a true polar traveler!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=29
PosMap=354

[QUEST138]
Nombre=Beyond the Hook
Desc=Do you really think a Reinforced Rod is enough to brave the treacherous rivers of the North? True fishing requires precision, patience... and a worthy tool. My uncle taught me the essentials, but I've taken his techniques a step further. If you want an Iron Fishing Rod, I'll need special parts. Bring that Reinforced Rod and obtain a Claw of the Azhurion. With those materials, I will forge you a rod that will not only catch fish, but tame the most stubborn fish. Do you accept the challenge?
DescFinal=There you have it: the Iron Fishing Rod. Lightweight, durable, and with a reel that won't jam even if you catch a river beast. My uncle Jacobo would say that 'fishing is patience,' but I say it's also science. Go out there and show the water who's boss.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=20
PosMap=61

[QUEST139]
Nombre=Winter strength
Desc=Welcome to this Snowy City! The cold here can kill you, you should always wear Winter Clothing to avoid suffering. If you manage to bring me 2 Gorilla Furs, I will give you one of these essential clothes for the area!
DescFinal=You have been very brave, with this you will be able to last a long time here!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=25
PosMap=354

[QUEST140]
Nombre=The skill of the Eyewarden
Desc=Your agility is impressive, but I can help you improve your magic. Near the Village of Eleuria, more precisely inside the Glacier Cave, you can find the Arctic Eyewarden, a creature whose dexterity is incredible. Bring the scroll and I will help you translate it to improve your spell.
DescFinal=I thought you wouldn't make it! Now dexterity is part of your body.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=30
PosMap=354

[QUEST141]
Nombre=The strength of Kadru
Desc=Your strength is admirable, but I can teach you how to improve your magic. Enter the Cave of the Nagas and show me your courage before the Kadrus that inhabit it, their strength demonstrates an opportunity to support our battle against darkness. Bring the scroll and I will help you translate it to improve your spell.
DescFinal=You have proven that the strength within you is enough to learn this spell, take this scroll, the shadows will fear your presence.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=28
PosMap=123

[QUEST142]
Nombre=The last Light
Desc=Oh Cleric! The light has brought you to me. Are you ready to learn one of the strongest healings of our kind? The sorceresses have usurped one of our sacred scrolls, finish them off, bring the scroll back and I will teach you the true healing power of the Light.
DescFinal=Congratulations! With this spell you can heal even the deepest wounds. May the Light continue on your path!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=26
PosMap=214

[QUEST143]
Nombre=Beginner cart (fisherman).
Desc=Get the necessary ingredients to prepare the great feast and in return you will receive the indications to build a cart for your merchandise.
DescFinal=Let's see ... I think this will help you a good time, remember that we can improve it when you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15

[QUEST144]
Nombre=Beginner cart (lumberjack).
Desc=If you want me to help you build an adequate cart for your work, you must venture in search of resources facing creatures that inhabit our lands, take this note, you have listed all the requirements, are you able to complete it? Success!
DescFinal=Let's see ... I think this will help you a good time, remember that we can improve it when you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15

[QUEST145]
Nombre=Beginner cart (miner).
Desc=You are the future of our work, be aware that our God Grodnar rewards us and protects us at all times, he commissioned me to teach future generations the technique to manufacture our precious wagons? To do this we must achieve its approval through cult, that is why I entrust you to search for these materials:
DescFinal=Let's see ... I think this will help you a good time, remember that we can improve it when you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=15

[QUEST146]
Nombre=Reinforced cart (fisherman).
Desc=Hey you! That wheelbarrow is too small for the amount of fish you bring, I think it's time to improve it. Comply with the next commission and see what I can do for you.
DescFinal=This insurance truck will be much more useful and will help you keep your merchandise for a longer time. Still we can keep improving it if you wish.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST147]
Nombre=Reinforced cart (lumberjack).
Desc=I see that you want to improve your old car, get the following insurance materials I can help you.
DescFinal=A reinforced car that exalts the profession, remembers that we can improve it whenever you want.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST148]
Nombre=Reinforced cart (miner).
Desc=I think it's time to improve that old car for a real car suitable for traveling the mines rails. Although I will need to make some materials.
DescFinal=Take! You'll see how easy it is with this car suitable for mines. Remember that you can keep improving it if you wish.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=25

[QUEST149]
Nombre=Elite cart (fisherman).
Desc=Do you need to change the truck?, What quickly do you progress,. Let's see with the following materials I think I can help you.
DescFinal=Here you have, without a doubt one of my best jobs!, Although I regret to tell you that from here you must find your own style.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=30

[QUEST150]
Nombre=Elite cart (lumberjack).
Desc=The old cart, I see that it has been very useful although it will not endure much more weight. I think we could build a new one if you get the following materials:
DescFinal=Take, you can load as many kilos of firewood as you want, although I have to inform you that I no longer have the tools to continue improving it.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=30

[QUEST151]
Nombre=Elite cart (miner).
Desc=Ohh, incredible! I am proud to see the use you have given to this car. If you get the materials we can climb it to the next level.
DescFinal=The terror of the rails will be called. Watch you will not find anything the same I hope you accompany you the rest of your tour because I do not think we can build something better.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=30

[QUEST152]
Nombre=Spell chest
Desc=This chest contains the best spells for the fittest warriors!
DescFinal=Good luck.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=1

[QUEST153]
Nombre=The Underground Challenge
Desc=The city's basements and drains are infested. You must eliminate a number of black and gray rats from your house, and venture to the drains where the Giant Rat rules, eliminating several of these dangerous specimens. This challenge requires patience, perseverance and skill, since only those who keep their subscription active will be able to progress each day. Upon completing this test, the reward will be unique and lasting: a special mount that will allow you to travel around the city with the strength of these creatures.
DescFinal=You have demonstrated perseverance and courage in the face of underground threats. Your perseverance and skill have not gone unnoticed. Have this Mount as recognition of your effort and dedication!
Repetible=1

[QUEST154]
Nombre=The seal of the Sun
Desc=The jade you carry is no mere stone. Each fragment you gathered was destined to remain separate, guarded by the ancient guardians of the Pyramid. Scarabs carved by hands that no longer exist still wander among the sands and tombs, carrying fragments of forgotten stories. By assembling these pieces, the puzzle was brought back to life, and with it, an energy the desert itself recognizes. It is a power that belongs neither to the living nor the dead: it can illuminate the mind, open hidden pathways, or awaken forces that should remain dormant. Whoever possesses the complete jade holds a link to secrets the sun and sand have guarded since ancient times. On its own, it can be unpredictable... but if given form, it can protect, reveal the hidden, or even guide those who are worthy. Now, that power can take shape. There is a mantle waiting for one who has been worthy to complete the work. Black as the desert night, golden as the light of its sun... a relic of a time when the ancient walked among the living. Give me the complete jade. Only then can the Mantle of the Fallen Sun be yours, and your participation in this ritual will be sealed forever.
DescFinal=Remember: the desert watches, and the secrets of the Fallen Sun are not revealed twice. May your path be marked by your courage and your wisdom.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18

[QUEST155]
Nombre=The Jade Puzzle
Desc=True jade doesn't break... it shatters to hide. In the Pyramid, the sands don't just cover tombs. They also conceal works that should never have been desecrated. There are creatures down there that don't attack out of instinct, but because of the burden they've carried since time immemorial. Scarabs carved by the ancients still walk among the ruined passageways, guardians of something they never understood. If fate is kind to you, the pieces will be reunited. And when that happens, the jade will speak for itself.
DescFinal=Each fragment bears the mark of the desert, but together they recapture the pulse of eternity. For years I believed this work was lost forever. The ancients were wise to separate it. My hands only do what the jade demands. It does not belong to me. Take it. The puzzle is complete. May its power be with you.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=1

[QUEST156]
Nombre=The Necklace of the Nameless King
Desc=I see the desert reflected in your eyes... you know what it's like to walk through cursed sands. Many years ago, a priceless necklace was buried alongside an unnamed king, deep within the Pyramid. It's not gold or silver that makes it special, but the curse that binds it to the dead. The mummies that wander there find no rest... one of them still wears the Ancient Necklace hanging from its withered neck. You must venture into the Pyramid and defeat mummies until you find it. There's no way of knowing which one wears it... the desert chooses. Bring me that necklace, and perhaps, just perhaps, we can unravel even more ancient secrets.
DescFinal=The mummies guarded it not out of loyalty, but as a curse. This object confirms my fears: the Pyramid still conceals fragments of an ancient power. You have done a great service, adventurer. Not everyone returns from there alive... and even fewer with a relic.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=18
PosMap=17

[QUEST157]
Nombre=Brushed planks.
Desc=I can brush all that wood for you, 10000 wood can give you 1000 planks
DescFinal=Look what a good job I have done. Here it is.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=1

[QUEST158]
Nombre=Brushed brushes.
Desc=I can brush all that wood for you, 10000 wood can give you 1000 planks
DescFinal=Look what a good job I have done. Here it is.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=1

[QUEST159]
Nombre=Empire helmet
Desc=I can forge a helmet for you, worthy of the forces of the empire. Only for clergy, paladins and warriors.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=40

[QUEST160]
Nombre=Secrets of the Eternal Desert
Desc=The necromantic energies emanating from the Mausoleum have guided us to the ancient Pyramid. There, among the sands and echoes of the past, lie Mummies imbued with a power far older than any known magic. Defeat the Mummies and search them for a Magic Note; you will also need the Egyptian Necklace worn by the sorcerer Kairo. Bring both items to me, and I will teach you a forgotten art: the power to Summon Mummies.
DescFinal=You've unraveled the secrets of ancient Egyptian necromancy. Your Summon Skeleton Warrior spell has been replaced with Summon Mummies, a power worthy of the ancient pharaohs!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=22
PosMap=16

[QUEST161]
Nombre=Bless!
Desc=If you bring me a Reliquary, I can bless it for some gold coins.
DescFinal=Your Reliquary was Blessed!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=23

[QUEST163]
Nombre=Cemetery guards
Desc=Those skeletons protect the Mausoleum during the night, if you manage to kill them, one day you will be able to enter!
DescFinal=How many bones!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=10
PosMap=30

[QUEST164]
Nombre=A special order
Desc=You must help me! King Tancred will be here in town soon and Governor Conrad has commissioned me to throw a great banquet for him and his troops... But I don't have enough fishermen to feed so many, much less a King! I know there is a special fish, the Bottom Grouper... it is elusive and can be a bit of work to get, but you should be able to catch it anywhere. If you manage to do it I will reward you, please help me!
DescFinal=You saved my neck! I will be eternally grateful. If you like to get more fish, talk to me again, there will always be hungry soldiers in Nix.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=12
PosMap=34

[QUEST165]
Nombre=Special suit
Desc=To enter the Cave of the Nagas, south of here, you will have to get a very Special costume... I can make one for you, if you get a particular tunic for me!
DescFinal=Good job, here's your reward.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=27
PosMap=557

[QUEST166]
Nombre=Clear the entrance
Desc=Hello, young adventurer, I need your help! That damned Laican has stolen the belongings of the inhabitants of Arghal, with your help we can recover everything! But first, clear the entrance, please!
DescFinal=Thank you very much! Have a little of this, it's the last thing I have left...
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=7
PosMap=418

[QUEST167]
Nombre=Entering the cave
Desc=You have managed to clear the entrance of those Hyenas and Wolves; Now we must check inside the Cave until we find the ferocious Laican. Complete this mission and see me again, I will reward you.
DescFinal=Have you seen it? Now is our time!
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=16

[QUEST168]
Nombre=Laican, the beast
Desc=Are you ready for this? It's time to go in and finally get this thing over with.
DescFinal=Thank you for your help! The people of Arghal will know your feat!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=17

[QUEST169]
Nombre=Help to return
Desc=I have spent a long time without returning to my beloved Ullathorpe, but now that I have found you, I need your help. Leaving this village to the south, the path is full of Scorpions, make your way through them to free the area .
DescFinal=You have survived! You have the strength necessary to help me accomplish my mission.
Repetible=1
RequiredLevel=13
PosMap=17

[QUEST170]
Nombre=Pyramid near the
Desc=From here you can see the Pyramid, near it you will come across two very powerful magical creatures, defeat them to secure the northern exit of this village.
DescFinal=Amazing! We can now leave this Village safely.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=16

[QUEST171]
Nombre=Final effort
Desc=Now that the exits of this village are clear, all that remains is to encourage us to leave the Desert. We must be careful with the spiders.
DescFinal=Your help has been fundamental, I will be grateful to you for life.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=17

[QUEST172]
Nombre=Under the North Winds
Desc=The ancient mages of the Threshold never finished the Mauve Flash. It was unstable, dangerous... and they abandoned it. But the eternal cold of the Frost Giants is capable of shaping it. That is why they have awakened, and that is why the skies have been corrupted. If you confront this source of power, the spell will grow with you. Go to the outskirts of Eleusis and prove the Threshold right about you: defeat the Frost Giants, unleash the northern winds, and some of the ice gems—the core of the power the giants guard.
DescFinal=The Threshold gave you knowledge. The North gave you strength.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=29
PosMap=354

[QUEST173]
Nombre=Lynn's Blood
Desc=If you have the courage to enter the Cave of the Nagas and extract a sample of their Blood, and also bring me a special potion, you will be rewarded with great power.
DescFinal=Great job, with this Flash you'll have incredible power!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=31
PosMap=517

[QUEST174]
Nombre=Persistent Pest Control
Desc=In recent days we have received reports of the presence of black rats in the basements of several Patreon Houses. These large, rarely traveled spaces often become ideal refuges for persistent pests. We cannot allow a distinguished property to fall into neglect. Descend into your basement, eliminate any creatures you find, and bring me proof that the situation has been properly controlled.
DescFinal=I see that you have fulfilled your task. The infestation has been reduced and, for the time being, your property is back in proper condition.
Repetible=1

[QUEST175]
Nombre=Anomalous Specimens
Desc=On rare occasions, an unusual specimen appears among the rats in the basement, recognizable by the pale tone of its tail. This is not a common pest, but an anomaly that very few house owners ever see. These specimens are elusive, and their appearance is unpredictable. If you are fortunate and skilled—enough to find one, bring me its tail as proof. The reward will match your effort.
DescFinal=I must admit, few manage to bring me a proof like this. You have shown patience and determination, qualities uncommon even among distinguished house owners. These specimens do not often reveal themselves, so consider this achievement exceptional. Should the anomaly appear again, I trust you will recognize it.
Repetible=1

[QUEST176]
Nombre=Lynn's Blood
Desc=If you have the courage to enter the Cave of the Nagas and extract a sample of their Blood, and also bring me a special potion, you will be rewarded with great power.
DescFinal=Great job, with this Flash you'll have incredible power!
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=33

[QUEST177]
Nombre=Some wood
Desc=If you are able to obtain 3000 firewood for me, I will be able to give you a good reward.
DescFinal=Excellent, have a little experience to improve your path, talk to me again if you want to progress even more.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=10

[QUEST178]
