Desc=If you are able to obtain 5000 Coal Ore and 5000 Silver Ore, I will be able to give you a good reward.
DescFinal=Excellent, have a little experience to improve your path, talk to me again if you want to progress even more.
Repetible=0
RequiredLevel=23

[QUEST187]
