[EN_SUGERENCIAS]
Sugerencia1=Did you know you can meditate simply by tapping your mana bar? Try it!
Sugerencia2=Did you know fighting NPCs increases your survival skill?
Sugerencia3=Did you know that by clicking on a user's name in the console you can send them a private message?
Sugerencia4=Did you know that with the /events command you can find out which event and when the next one will be? Keep track of your time!
Sugerencia5=Did you know you can disable the game's default cursor in Options?
Sugerencia6=Did you know that to talk globally you just have to enter ";" before your message?

